The hive holds valuables!
The hive's inhabitants sting and bite the hero's exposed flesh!

The vermin sizzle and pop as the hive burns to ash.

Treasure lies in the gore-filled basin!
The hero's scars weep and open when bathed in the crimson fluid!
This bloody artifact invites ailment!

Burning the blood stings the nostrils and turns the stomach.

Cloth is used to protect fragile flesh against the barbs and mandibles.

Relief washes over the party as no fiend survived the resulting inferno.

Mouldering evidence of sick and debased pass times!
A stack of bets is found by the instruments of torture!
The macabre remains awaken suppressed desires!
Images of debauched games leap unbidden into the mind!

The hero cracks open the skull to reveal loot!  Who put it here..?

Apparently these ghoulish flowers are harmless.
The potting soil reveals its treasure!
The blossoms reek of death, pestilence and unfathomable nightmares!
A map is nestled between the thorns and blossoms!
Thorns hook into the flesh, a cloying sap seeps into the hero's blood!
STRING
The flowers visibly surge with growth! But nothing further occurs.

The rotting food makes the hero ill.
Some things are obviously best left alone!

Precise use of herbs purifies the tainted remains.

A single sip uncorks a disturbing new habit!

The hero breaks the empty bottle and discovers a treasure map!
